, effective as of September 21, 2011, the Employment Agreement is hereby amended as follows:
NOW, THEREFORE
 
1.           Section 2 of the Employment Agreement is amended by adding the following sentence to end thereof to read as follows:
 
Notwithstanding the foregoing, effective as of September 21, 2011, the Employment Term is extended for a Renewal Term ending on September 21, 2014 (the End Date), unless sooner terminated in accordance with Section 5 below, and the Employment Term shall not be subject to automatic extension following the End Date.
 
