Item 7.01 Regulation FD Disclosure.
 
On March 1, 2012, Ascena Retail Group, Inc. (the Company) hosted an investor conference call to discuss the Companys results of operations for its second quarter ended January 28, 2012 and certain other information, including the contents of the Companys press release dated March 1, 2012 which was furnished to the Securities and Exchange Commission on Form 8-K on March 1, 2012. The conference call was pre-announced and was available to the public through live teleconference. A transcript of the conference call is furnished herewith as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated by reference herein.
 
