Item 8.01 Other Events
 
On March 8, 2012, Ascena Retail Group, Inc. issued a press release announcing that its Board of Directors approved a two-for-one common stock split payable on April 3, 2012 to stockholders of record at the close of business on March 20, 2012. A copy of this press release is furnished as Exhibit No. 99.1 to this Form 8-K and is incorporated by reference into this item 8.01.
 
