The term loan is going to be a six-year term loan. Obviously, we expect to pay that a lot faster than six years, hopefully a couple of years. But the terms on that loan, again, it is a $300 million term loan and we don't have the final numbers yet, but indication purposes from our bankers tell us that it could likely be in the range of LIBOR plus 325 to 350 basis points.
