SECTION 1.05. All references herein to the Company and the Subsidiaries shall be deemed to be references to such Persons, and all the representations and warranties of the Company and the other Loan Parties contained in this Agreement and the other Loan Documents shall be deemed made, in each case, after giving effect to the Acquisition and the other Transactions to occur on the Second Restatement Effective Date, unless the context otherwise requires.
