provided
 
above and confirming that the other requirements of this clause (p) have been satisfied; that a purchase or acquisition (in one transaction or a series of transactions) of all or substantially all the assets of any Person or of a business unit, division, product line or line of business of any Person, may be only made in reliance on clause (h) of this Section and not on this clause (p).
