THOMSON REUTERS STREETEVENTS
EDITED TRANSCRIPT
ASNA - Q4 2012 Ascena Retail Group, Inc. Earnings
Conference Call
 
EVENT DATE/TIME: SEPTEMBER 19, 2012 / 01:00PM GMT
 
OVERVIEW:
ASNA reported FY12 reported sales of $3.4b and adjusted net income of $214m or $1.34 per diluted share. 4Q12 reported net sales was $940m and reported net income from continuing operations including certain items was $11.2m or $0.07 per diluted share. Expects FY ending July 2013 sales to be $5b and adjusted EPS to be $1.45-1.55.
 
 
 
 
CORPORATE PARTICIPANTS
Allison Townsend
ICR - IR
David Jaffe
Ascena Retail Group Inc - President and CEO
Armand Correia
Ascena Retail Group Inc - EVP and CFO
 
