It's a fact that the plus sized customer wants to wear many of the same fashions as her skinny trends. But she wants to be trend right with a fit that is both comfortable and flattering. Our mission evolves from this as we seek to make her look stylish and feel sexy, confident and happy. Pictured here is one of our strip centers, located in Madison, Mississippi.
 
