Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
 
On December 5, 2012, Ascena Retail Group, Inc. (the Company) issued a press release disclosing material non-public information regarding its results of operations for its fiscal first quarter ended October 27, 2012. The Company also reaffirmed its earnings per diluted share guidance for its full fiscal year ending July 27, 2013. A copy of this press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K and is incorporated by reference into this Item 2.02.
 
