For the second quarter of 2013, earnings per diluted share from continuing operations share, while earnings from discontinued operations were $0.06 per share. This compares to diluted earnings per share from continuing operations of $0.40 per share in Fiscal 2012. Adjusted earnings per share from continuing operations on this basis was $0.26 per diluted share for the second quarter (see Non-GAAP Financial Results section of this release for additional comments on adjustments).
