Average Availability
 
 means, with respect to any period, (a) the sum of Utilization for each day during such period divided by (b) the number of days in such period.  means, on any day, an amount equal to (a) the total Credit Exposure of all Lenders on such day, divided by (b) the total Revolving Commitments in effect on such day.
