 means, at any time, the Inventory of a Loan Party which the Administrative Agent determines in its Permitted Discretion is eligible as the basis for (i) the extension of Revolving Loans and Swingline Loans and (ii) the issuance of Letters of Credit. Without limiting the Administrative Agents discretion provided herein, Eligible Inventory shall not include any Inventory:
Eligible Inventory
 
(a)  which is not subject to a first priority perfected Lien in favor of the Administrative Agent (for the benefit of the Lender Parties);
 
