SECTION 6.05. The Company will not, and will not permit any Subsidiary to, sell, transfer, lease or otherwise dispose of any asset, including any Equity Interest owned by it, nor will the Company permit any Subsidiary to issue any additional Equity Interests in such Subsidiary (other than to the Company or any other Subsidiary in compliance with Section 6.04, and other than directors qualifying shares and other nominal amounts of Equity Interests that are required to be held by other Persons under applicable law), except:
