www.streetevents.com
|
Contact Us
 
 
 
 
 Neely Tamminga
- Piper Jaffray - Senior Research Analyst 
 
 And that's really the last major hole. I mean you, the Head of Sourcing, you've done --
 
  
 David Jaffe
- Ascena Retail Group, Inc. - CEO 
 
 maurices and I had their CMO filled a couple months ago with woman named Erin Stern with terrific background. So, we feel pretty good. Not only have we filled the positions, but we brought in Major League talents talent and I think they're going to do great job in their roles.
 
 
